  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Following Rainwater harvesting champions in Ethiopia, Kenya, Uganda</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">INT</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">R-D</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The video should be appealing to a large audience of stakeholders and inspiring them about the work RAIN does by showing 3 projects in 3 countries. In order to appeal to a broad viewer audience the video will explain the essence of these projects, but will not deeply cover the technical aspects of these projects. Instead the video will focus on people who are &#x2018;champions&#x2019; of rainwater harvesting within their community.</narrative>
